

# CHARGY! 

Welcome to the chargy project. Most boring wireless phone chargers light up when your device is charging, BORING. We already know when we are charging our devices. Internet of things future people want to know when other people are charging! Name your chargyr, trade names with friends, get a sweet light show when someone is charging. 


![Chargyr](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3605312/104239526-7ccd3d00-540f-11eb-8e29-a50b94db1b3f.png)


This project is in early development. 


